pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `canbo` ( `MACANBO` char(9) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `MANHANKHAUTHUONGTRU` char(9) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `TENTAIKHOAN` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `MATKHAU` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `LOAICANBO` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`MACANBO`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf32 COLLATE=utf32_unicode_ci;
